# Hoe of Honor — Passive Harvest Row
# Scans 9 blocks along the X axis at the current position
# Called from passive_harvest.mcfunction with X already at -4 offset
# @s = player (for mainhand context), position = start of row

function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~1 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~2 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~3 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~4 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~5 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~6 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~7 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
execute positioned ~8 ~ ~ run function evercraft:artifacts/mythical_tools/hoe_of_honor/harvest_single
